Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.87,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,哪怕受到伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.20,0:02:29.79,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,胸中想要守护的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.71,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,在燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.63,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,未来就在身边
