Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:40.18,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,甩开泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:45.18,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,向这片天空起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.52,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,来吧 挥动翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.81,0:02:51.60,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,鼓起无敌的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.02,0:02:54.52,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,不再犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:57.28,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,踏出第一步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.99,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,用力伸出双手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:04.95,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,向着谁都不曾知晓的那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:08.29,Opening - CN,,0,0,0,,虔诚祈愿
