Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.11,0:22:30.16,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,-15)}又倍感痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.16,0:22:39.46,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,尽管如此 我们也要生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.67,0:22:45.71,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,就算受伤 就算流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:50.97,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,明天也仍将到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:56.56,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,不要哭泣 无论到哪里
